data.description: Charming 3-bed, 2-bath home with 1,811 sqft of living space on a generous 7,364 sqft lot in the heart of Rosenberg, TX. This well-maintained residence offers a comfortable layout, showcasing spacious bedrooms and inviting common areas. Conveniently located near amenities, this home is perfect for first-time homebuyers and savvy investors alike. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home or a lucrative investment property!
